==Dialogue==
{{Dialogue Start}}
:'''Simulated Universe:''' You meet a mechanical lifeform. It seems to be skilled in repairing Curios.
:'''Simulated Universe:''' "Click... Click..."
:'''Simulated Universe:''' It gestures for you to let it repair your treasures.
;(If embarking on the Path of [[Simulated Universe/Paths#Abundance|Abundance]] in a Simulated Universe Expansion)
:{{Icon/Dark|Path Abundance Small.png|20}} Express friendship to the inorganic life. &mdash; Obtain 1 random damageable Curio(s).
:;(Obtain a Damageable Curio)
;(If embarking on the Path of [[Simulated Universe/Paths#Elation|Elation]] in a Simulated Universe Expansion)
:{{Icon/Dark|Path Elation Small.png|20}} Have a pleasant inorganic exchange! &mdash; Replace all Curios with damageable Curios.
:;(Discard all Curios in exchange for the same number of random Damageable Curios)
:{{DIcon|Star}} Repair a damaged Curio. &mdash; Spend 50 Cosmic Fragment(s) and repair 1 damaged Curio.
:;(Lose 50 Cosmic Fragments)
:;(Repair 3 Curios)
:{{DIcon|Star}} Repair all damaged Curios. &mdash; Spend 100 Cosmic Fragment(s) and repair all damaged Curios.
:;(Lose 100 Cosmic Fragments)
:;(Repair all Curios)
:{{DIcon|Star}} Leave. &mdash; You don't need this.
{{Dialogue End}}

